OL,3,CMinister makes emotional pilgrimage to
OL,4,CJapan to honour POW father
OL,6,FDespite his ordeal he was not bitter
OL,7,Ftowards the Japanese and told his
OL,8,Ffamily he wanted to return to the
OL,9,Fcountry one day to experience it
OL,10,Fduring peacetime.
OL,12,FHe never returned, however, as he died
OL,13,Fin 1963 aged 45.
OL,15,FRev Gilmour was just seven when his
OL,16,Ffather passed away, and for the
OL,17,Ffollowing 60 years he longed to fulfil
OL,18,Fhis father's dream and visit Hiroshima.
