OL,6,F"So, in a sense, my life was dependent
OL,7,Fon a horrendous event that my father
OL,8,Fsurvived."
OL,10,FRev Gilmour said his father had a
OL,11,Fstrong desire to survive the war and
OL,12,Fget home to Glasgow.
OL,14,F"He only had one sister and she had
OL,15,Fdied just before the war of scarlet
OL,16,Ffever and his mother was a widow and
OL,17,Fhad nobody else in the world," he said.
