OL,6,FPrivate Gilmour was 27 when he
OL,7,Freturned to Glasgow and went on to
OL,8,Fwork for a building materials supply
OL,9,Fmerchant, and later the publishing
OL,10,Fhouse Collins.
OL,12,F"He and my mother had three sons, Jim,
OL,13,FStewart and myself," Rev Gilmour said.
OL,15,F"He spoke about his wartime
OL,16,Fexperiences publicly only once after
OL,17,Fhe was asked to give a talk at his
OL,18,Fhome church, Chalmers Church in
OL,19,FGlasgow.
